= Helios Mission Operations Guide

== Overview ==
The Helios crew relies on this Creole guide whenever updating systems referenced in the `mission-wiki.wiki` knowledge hub or the structured outline stored in `mission-outline.opml`. Coordination with navigation is tracked through the <<celestial-navigation-notes.adoc,Asciidoc navigation log>>.

=== Roles ===
* **Flight Director** -- approves burn plans from //navigation-theory.tex//.
* **Communications Lead** -- verifies network diagrams in {{{mission-network.dot}}}.
* **Onboard Scientist** -- updates observation payload manifests mirrored in [[../stellar-observation.docbook|DocBook archive]].

=== Shift Checklist ===
# Sync timeline with {{{mission-summary.metamd}}}.
# Review telemetry anomalies flagged in [[../telemetry-events.jsonl|JSONL stream]].
# Update OODA loop board; crosslink tasks to [[../mission-briefing.dokuwiki#ActionItems|Briefing Action Items]].

