=== Anomaly Response ===
If the telemetry queue exceeds thresholds:
* Capture raw packets in the {{telemetry-events.ndjson}} log.
* Annotate findspots in the `engineering-notes.rest` document.
* Notify knowledge archivists to append a narrative to `explorer-journal.fb2`.

